---

<%= partial "shared/ignore_actions" %>

```yaml
default: &defaults
  ignore_actions:
    - "ApplicationController#is_up"
    - "MyBackgroundWorker#perform"
```

If you use Sinatra or any other framework, use the HTTP method and path you used to specify your route, for example:

```yaml
default: &defaults
  ignore_actions:
    - "GET /pages/:id"
    - "POST /pages/create"
```

You can also configure ignore actions via an environment variable.

```bash
export APPSIGNAL_IGNORE_ACTIONS="ApplicationController#is_up,MyBackgroundWorker#perform"
```
